SILVER (PAL FRENCH)
COUNTRY .... EUROPE
LANGUAGE .... FRENCH AUDIO WITH SUBS IN FRENCH, ITALIAN, PORTUGESE
RELEASE DATE .... 01/30/01

Terror grips the land. The powerful and evil Sorcerer Silver has abducted the women of Jarrah for his treacherous purposes. Take control as David, a simple hero on a quest to save his beloved and defeat the almighty Silver. But it won't be easy. In order to succeed you'll need to recruit allies, master swordplay, learn the art of magic, and venture through hostile worlds teeming with Silver's corrupt followers.